      "text": "Teaching practices that schools adopt can be a sophisticated synthesis of research-based strategies from different programs, taking the best parts from many, rather than using the whole of one. Rather than simply taking programs as they are, school teams might instead analyse the parts, selecting best practice strategies that align with who they are as a community. For example, a  collection of strategies might come together to form a school’s pedagogical approach. "
